OL,3,C'He was loved by so many': Mum of
OL,4,Calleged murder victim pays tribute
OL,6,FThe mother of a man who was allegedly
OL,7,Fkilled in Plymouth has paid tribute to
OL,8,Fhim, saying he was 'loved by so many
OL,9,Fpeople'.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,12,Fproperty on Embankment Road on Monday
OL,13,F4 May where Harry Jackson, 28, was
OL,14,Ffound with serious injuries but later
OL,15,Fdied at the scene.
OL,17,FA 57-year-old Plymouth man has since
OL,18,Fbeen charged with Harry's murder and
OL,19,Fis due to go on trial in October.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
