OL,3,C'He was loved by so many': Mum of
OL,4,Calleged murder victim pays tribute
OL,6,FMark Carpenter, of Embankment Road,
OL,7,Fdid not appear for a hearing at
OL,8,FPlymouth Crown Court today, Monday 11
OL,9,FMay.
OL,11,FJudge Robert Linford said he will
OL,12,Fappear on 22 June for a plea and trial
OL,13,Fpreparation hearing.
OL,15,FPaying tribute to Harry, mum Sue Jones
OL,16,FEdwards posted on social media: "I
OL,17,Fcan't thank the thousands of people
OL,18,Fsending so much love for him. It truly
OL,19,Fshows the impact he had on so many
OL,20,Fpeople."
OL,26,@xD@aOU|D@HO]
