OL,3,C'He was loved by so many': Mum of
OL,4,Calleged murder victim pays tribute
OL,6,FMs Jones Edwards is now planning
OL,7,Fevents to remember her son's life,
OL,8,Fincluding on The Hoe in Plymouth,
OL,9,Fwhich she described as his favourite
OL,10,Fplace.
OL,12,FShe added: "This was the last place we
OL,13,Fwent together. We laughed so much.
OL,14,FHarry loved Plymouth and I need
OL,15,FPlymouth and the whole world to feel
OL,16,Fmy pain and come together.
OL,26,@tD@LOU
