PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1778508672
OL,3,C'He was loved by so many': Mum of
OL,4,Calleged murder victim pays tribute
OL,6,F"You can light a candle for him, come
OL,7,Fand tell me your stories good, bad,
OL,8,Ffunny or sad. I need as many as many
OL,9,Fmemories as possible for his little
OL,10,Fboys."
OL,12,FMs Jones Edwards said Harry loved
OL,13,Fmotorbikes and so she is asking local
OL,14,Fbikers to ride past his house as a way
OL,15,Fto pay tribute to her son and remember
OL,16,Fhim.
OL,18,FShe added: "He was loved by so many
OL,19,Fpeople his boys need to remember every
OL,20,Fsingle thing about him."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@FO]zD@LOU|D@XO]
